I am an expert in Mind-Body Pain Syndrome.  I work with people in physical pain who are ready to explore the mind-body connection who struggle not only with pain but weight, exhaustion, depression, worry and anxiety.

What separates my services from other people who work with pain is I’ve been there.  I used to experience so much pain it would actually make me physically ill.  I know what works and how only addressing the physical doesn’t always get to the root of the issue.  Because of this my clients receive proven methods saving time and money on therapies, drugs, doctors, and unnecessary surgeries that don’t always get to the underlying cause.

As a result, those who get coached by me learn how to heal their pain and create a life they love.

Would you like to know more?
